    "transliteration": "AlqariAAatu",
    "translation": "The Sudden Calamity!",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "ref": "101:2",
    "arabic": "مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
    "transliteration": "Ma alqariAAatu",
    "translation": "What is the Sudden Calamity?",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "ref": "101:3",
    "arabic": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
    "transliteration": "Wama adraka ma alqariAAatu",
    "translation": "And what do you know what the Sudden Calamity is?",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "ref": "101:4",
    "arabic": "يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ",
    "transliteration": "Yawma yakoonu alnnasu kaalfarashi almabthoothi",
    "translation": "It is a Day when mankind shall be like the scattered moths,",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "ref": "101:5",
    "arabic": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ",
    "transliteration": "Watakoonu aljibalu kaalAAihni almanfooshi",
    "translation": "And the mountains like fluffed up wool.",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "ref": "101:6",
    "arabic": "فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
    "transliteration": "Faamma man thaqulat mawazeenuhu",
    "translation": "That person, then, who weighs heavy [with good deeds] on the scales,",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "ref": "101:7",
    "arabic": "فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ",
    "transliteration": "Fahuwa fee AAeeshatin radiyatin",
    "translation": "[That person] shall have a pleasant life.",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "ref": "101:8",
    "arabic": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
    "transliteration": "Waamma man khaffat mawazeenuhu",
    "translation": "And that person, who weighs light [because of bad deeds] on the scales,",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "ref": "101:9",
    "arabic": "فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ",
    "transliteration": "Faommuhu hawiyatun",
    "translation": "The Abyss then shall be his home.",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "ref": "101:10",
    "arabic": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ",
    "transliteration": "Wama adraka ma hiyah",
    "translation": "And what do you understand what it [the Abyss] is?",
    "notes": ""
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "ref": "101:11",
    "arabic": "نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ",
    "transliteration": "Narun hamiyatun",
    "translation": "A Fire intensely hot.",
    "notes": "Described in this Qur’aanic Chapter is what would happen when the Hour (the time when the present world will end and the Hereafter begin) arrives."
